---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="About Us - MDMY Blog"
  description="Learn more about our blog, our mission, and the team behind MDMY."
>
  <section class="max-w-3xl mx-auto py-8">
    <h1 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold mb-6">About MDMY Blog</h1>
    
    <div class="prose prose-lg dark:prose-invert max-w-none">
      <p>
        Welcome to MDMY Blog, where we share insights, tutorials, and news about technology, 
        design, and digital innovation. Our mission is to provide high-quality content that 
        educates, inspires, and keeps you informed about the latest trends and best practices.
      </p>
      
      <h2>Our Mission</h2>
      <p>
        At MDMY Blog, we're dedicated to creating valuable content that helps our readers 
        stay ahead in the rapidly evolving digital landscape. Whether you're a developer, 
        designer, marketer, or tech enthusiast, our goal is to deliver content that matters to you.
      </p>
      
      <h2>Our Team</h2>
      <p>
        We're a team of passionate writers, developers, and industry experts committed to 
        sharing our knowledge and experience with our community. Each member of our team 
        brings unique perspectives and expertise to create comprehensive and insightful content.
      </p>
      
      <h2>Contact Us</h2>
      <p>
        Have questions, feedback, or want to collaborate with us? We'd love to hear from you!
        You can reach out to us at <a href="mailto:contact@yourdomain.com">contact@yourdomain.com</a>.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>